             <string>
fπ = 1 / (2π Rπ Cπ)
fµ = 1 / (2π Rµ Cµ)

fπ || fµ ≤ fH ≤ min(fπ, fµ)

Conservative:
fH = fπ || fµ 

Cx = (1/Rµ) [1/(2πfH) - RπCπ] - Cµ
Cµ,total = Cµ + Cx</string>
